### SG-036 P1-core-read — 10 endpoint coverage 보강 (Cycle 10, 2026-05-12)
###
### 배경:
###   Cycle 9 baseline: .http 69 unique vs router 137 unique → coverage 19.7%.
###   본 cycle: P1-core-read 10건 (`GET /api/v1/{resource}/{id}`) 보강.
###   목표: 69 → 79 unique, mismatch 136 → 126 (10 감소).
###
### Scope:
###   P1-core-read 10건 — 모든 entity 의 read-by-id endpoint.
###   사전 조건: list endpoint 호출하여 실재 id 확보 후 read 호출 패턴.
###
### Schema 정합 (BO src/models/schemas.py 기준):
###   각 ResponseModel 은 ApiResponse[{Resource}Response] 형태.
###   RBAC: get_current_user (viewer 이상). users 만 admin 권장.
###
### Cycle 10 priority matrix (P1-core-read 10건):
###   1. GET /api/v1/series/{id}
###   2. GET /api/v1/competitions/{id}
###   3. GET /api/v1/players/{id}
###   4. GET /api/v1/users/{id}              (admin 권장)
###   5. GET /api/v1/blind-structures/{id}
###   6. GET /api/v1/payout-structures/{id}
###   7. GET /api/v1/flights/{id}
###   8. GET /api/v1/hands/{id}
###   9. GET /api/v1/configs/{id}
###  10. GET /api/v1/decks/{id}
###
### Source: SG-036 Spec_Gap_Registry §4.5 + integration-tests/_audit/sg036-cycle9/

@host = http://localhost:18001
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}
@viewer_token = {{$dotenv VIEWER_JWT}}

# 사전 조건 변수 (실행 전 list 호출로 id 확보 또는 .env 주입)
@series_id = {{$dotenv TEST_SERIES_ID}}
@competition_id = {{$dotenv TEST_COMPETITION_ID}}
@player_id = {{$dotenv TEST_PLAYER_ID}}
@user_id = {{$dotenv TEST_USER_ID}}
@blind_structure_id = {{$dotenv TEST_BLIND_STRUCTURE_ID}}
@payout_structure_id = {{$dotenv TEST_PAYOUT_STRUCTURE_ID}}
@flight_id = {{$dotenv TEST_FLIGHT_ID}}
@hand_id = {{$dotenv TEST_HAND_ID}}
@config_id = {{$dotenv TEST_CONFIG_ID}}
@deck_id = {{$dotenv TEST_DECK_ID}}

### 71.1 GET /api/v1/series/{id} — read series by id (viewer OK)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/series/{{series_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답:
# 200 OK
# { "data": SeriesResponse, "meta": {} }
# 404 NOT_FOUND = SERIES_NOT_FOUND.
# RBAC: get_current_user.

### 71.2 GET /api/v1/competitions/{id} — read competition (viewer OK)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/competitions/{{competition_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답: ApiResponse[CompetitionResponse].
# 404 = COMPETITION_NOT_FOUND.

### 71.3 GET /api/v1/players/{id} — read player (viewer OK)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/players/{{player_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답: ApiResponse[PlayerResponse].
# 404 = PLAYER_NOT_FOUND.

### 71.4 GET /api/v1/users/{id} — read user (admin OK)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users/{{user_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상 응답: ApiResponse[UserResponse].
# RBAC: admin 권장 (PII 보호). 404 = USER_NOT_FOUND.

### 71.4b GET /api/v1/users/{id} — viewer 거부 (403)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users/{{user_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답: 403 Forbidden, AUTH_INSUFFICIENT_ROLE (admin only 시).
# 또는 200 (BO 가 viewer 허용 시) — 실측 후 BO 정합 결정.

### 71.5 GET /api/v1/blind-structures/{id} — read blind structure (viewer OK)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/blind-structures/{{blind_structure_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답: ApiResponse[BlindStructureResponse] (levels 포함).
# Final Table 진입 시 blind level 화면 호출.

### 71.6 GET /api/v1/payout-structures/{id} — read payout structure (viewer OK)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/payout-structures/{{payout_structure_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답: ApiResponse[PayoutStructureResponse].
# 토너먼트 상금 구조 조회.

### 71.7 GET /api/v1/flights/{id} — read flight (viewer OK)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/flights/{{flight_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답: ApiResponse[FlightResponse] (clock/blind/tables 메타).
# Flight 상세 진입.

### 71.8 GET /api/v1/hands/{id} — read hand (viewer OK)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/hands/{{hand_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답: ApiResponse[HandResponse] (actions/players 메타).
# Hand 상세 조회 (replay 진입).

### 71.9 GET /api/v1/configs/{id} — read config (admin)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/configs/{{config_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상 응답: ApiResponse[ConfigResponse] (key/value 메타).
# 운영 config 조회. admin 권장.

### 71.10 GET /api/v1/decks/{id} — read deck (viewer OK)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/decks/{{deck_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답: ApiResponse[DeckResponse] (RFID registry 메타).
# Deck register 후 verification 호출.
